<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7987381>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Pupal exuviae of Chaetocladius spp. Frontal apotome of: A) C. cf. callauensis sp. n.; B) C. mantetensis; C) C. cf. guardiolei sp. n. Distribution pattern of dorsocentral setae on thorax of: D) C. melaleucus; E) C. perennis; F) C. guisseti; G) C. mantetensis; H) C. bitusiki; I) C. cf. laminatus; J) C. cf. callauensis sp. n.; K) C. cf. guardiolei sp. n; L) C. cf. parerai sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7987381/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

